Scope of this license:

  - The thesis document (LaTeX source in memoria/source/ and compiled PDF
    memoria/Memoria.pdf) is licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0.
  - The source code (spark/ worker, scripts and pipeline; the backend
    and frontend hosted in separate repositories) is licensed under
    CC BY-NC 4.0 for academic and non-commercial use.
  - The figures and metric reports (reports/, memoria/source/*.png) that
    contain no identifiable patient information are licensed under
    CC BY-NC 4.0.
  - The original undergraduate material in original-project/ (Memoria
    v1, scripts and poster by Marc Link Cladera and Antonio Contestí
    Coll, supervised by Dr. Miquel Miró Nicolau, UIB) is licensed under
    CC BY-NC 4.0.
  - Third-party material (datasets NODE21, VinDr-CXR, ChestX-ray14,
    JSRT, PadChest, Open-I, TBX11K; reference implementations such as
    the Behrendt et al. NODE21 submission; pre-trained weights from
    torchvision and Ultralytics) retains its original license. This
    work only references and evaluates such material; it does not
    redistribute it.

